		<div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-96 h-96 bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-400/20 to-cyan-600/20 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>

		<div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-8">
			<!-- Hero Section -->
			<div class="text-center mb-12">
				<div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-20 h-20 bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-lg rounded-2xl shadow-xl mb-6 border border-white/20">
					<svg class="w-10 h-10 text-indigo-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
						<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h8a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-3 7h3m-3 4h3m-6-4h.01M9 16h.01" />
					</svg>
				</div>
				<h1 class="text-5xl sm:text-6xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-900 via-indigo-900 to-gray-900 bg-clip-text text-transparent mb-4 tracking-tight">
					Levantapedidos
				</h1>
				<p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
					Generador inteligente de pedidos sugeridos basado en an√°lisis predictivo de ventas
